item.title: Pure guide pleas
item.dc:creator: @Phaze_One Fuscate
item.description:
@Phaze_One wrote:

If you want to train a 99 str pure with low defence on f2p, you’re fucked. The most likely place for a f2p training spot would be the stronghold of security fighting giant spiders/flesh crawlers or seeking out cockroaches in that other dungeon. But almost all of those are high level monsters and you would be running to the bank every 10 minutes or so. If you were p2p a good training spot would be soul wars. You get xp for fighting other players and zeal points can be used to buy large amounts of strength xp/prayer xp.
